I usually dont really like heavily nested for loops:

for i in some_iterable:
    if condition_0(i):
        a.append(i)

I rather add a continue to skip iterations in the loop and have less levels of indentation:

for i in some_iterable:
    if condition_0(i):
        continue
    a.append(i)
